data.text:
Patricia Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Patricia is recorded 398,383 times globally, ranking it as the 66th most common name worldwide.

Patricia is most prevalent in United States of America, with 55,947 occurrences, making it the 61th most popular name in the country.
